header(class="sticky top-0 z-20 border-b border-zinc-200 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950/95")
    div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-5 py-4 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
        div
            div(class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-globe")
                span Domains
            h1(class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 도메인 관리
        button(type="button", (click)="load()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
            i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right")
            span 새로고침

main(class="space-y-5 px-5 py-5")
    div(*ngIf="loading()", class="h-32 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400") 정보를 불러오는 중입니다.
    div(*ngIf="error()", class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300") {{error()}}

    div(*ngIf="!loading() && !error()", class="space-y-5")
        div(*ngIf="!cloudflare().enabled", class="rounded-md border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-amber-800 dark:border-amber-900/70 dark:bg-amber-950/30 dark:text-amber-200")
            i(class="fa-solid fa-circle-info mr-2")
            | Cloudflare 자동 연동은 꺼져 있습니다. 이 화면은 수동 domain/proxy 관리 상태를 계속 보여줍니다.
        section(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 md:grid-cols-4")
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-4 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Cloudflare
                p(class="mt-2 truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{cloudflare().primary || '-'}}
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-4 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Zones
                p(class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{zones().length}}
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-4 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Service domains
                p(class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{domains().length}}
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-4 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Certificates
                p(class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{certificates().length}}

        section(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 xl:grid-cols-[1fr_420px]")
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                    h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Service routing
                div(class="overflow-x-auto")
                    table(class="min-w-full divide-y divide-zinc-100 text-sm dark:divide-zinc-800")
                        thead(class="bg-zinc-50 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400")
                            tr
                                th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") Domain
                                th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") Service
                                th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") Port
                                th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") Proxy
                                th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") SSL
                        tbody(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                            tr(*ngFor="let item of domains()")
                                td(class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{item.domain}}
                                td(class="px-4 py-3 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300") {{item.service_name || '-'}}
                                td(class="px-4 py-3 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300") {{item.port}}
                                td(class="px-4 py-3 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300") {{item.proxy_type}}
                                td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                    span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(item.ssl_mode)") {{item.ssl_mode}}
                            tr(*ngIf="domains().length === 0")
                                td(colspan="5", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 연결된 도메인 없음

            div(class="space-y-5")
                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                    div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Cloudflare 영역
                    div(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                        div(*ngFor="let zone of zones()", class="px-4 py-3")
                            div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3")
                                p(class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{zone.domain}}
                                span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(zone.enabled)") {{zone.enabled ? '사용 중' : '꺼짐'}}
                            p(class="mt-1 truncate text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{zone.zone_id}}
                        div(*ngIf="zones().length === 0", class="px-4 py-8 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 등록된 zone 없음

                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                    div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Certificates
                    div(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                        div(*ngFor="let cert of certificates()", class="px-4 py-3")
                            div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3")
                                p(class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{cert.domain || cert.cert_path}}
                                span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(cert.status)") {{cert.status}}
                            p(class="mt-1 truncate text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{cert.mode}} · {{formatDate(cert.expires_at)}}
                        div(*ngIf="certificates().length === 0", class="px-4 py-8 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 인증서 기록 없음
